yngealized version when learning Arabic.%0a%3c Source: Shehata, A. (2015). Native English Speakers’ perception and production of Arabic consonants. The Routledge Handbook of Arabic Second Language Acquisition, 2(9), 24-47. doi:10.4324/9781315674261-4%0a%3c  %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a%3c (:Category:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
